### Create pick wave for accepted orders
POST http://localhost:8080/api/fulfillment/pick-waves
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: local-create-pick-wave

{
  "deliveryDate": "2030-12-31",
  "deliveryZone": "EAST"
}

### List pick waves
GET http://localhost:8080/api/fulfillment/pick-waves
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-pick-waves

### Get pick wave
GET http://localhost:8080/api/fulfillment/pick-waves/{{pickWaveId}}
X-Correlation-Id: local-get-pick-wave

### List SLA-risk dispatch jobs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/fulfillment/sla-risk
X-Correlation-Id: local-fulfillment-sla-risk
